{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"181651-ke-sabhta-kha-gel","title":"के सभटा खा गेल?","description":"जंगल एत्तेक साफ कोना अछि? आउ, पता करी जे केना जङलमे किछु व्यर्थ नहि होइत अछि।","language":"Maithili","langCode":"mai","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Raghu Kumar"],"illustrators":["Rohan Chakravarty"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/181651-ke-sabhta-kha-gel"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/188968/size3/715cc0ac513fbf98008ab8be6fa089d2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/188968/size6/715cc0ac513fbf98008ab8be6fa089d2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48918/size6/3f3ac741980cc208e814de67c6869529.jpg","text":"जंगलमे किछु बेकार नहि होइत अछि।\nकिछु नहि!\nसभ किछु साफ भऽ जाइत छैक।\nसभ किछु!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48919/size6/b58c99034969bc162cef06fd075a954a.jpg","text":"जखन तेंदुआ अपन खेनाइ छोड़ि दैत अछि,\nतऽ बचलाहा के खाइत अछि?\nगिद्ध आ लकड़बग्घा!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48920/size6/a15b1e625ddf40765e8e5c003e3c2b46.jpg","text":"आ भूखल जंगली सूगर।\nघुर्र-घुर्र! घुर्र-घुर्र!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48921/size6/c114039e78138e4cd6fff550955aa731.jpg","text":"जखन\nगिद्ध आ लकड़बग्घा खेनाइ बर्बाद करैत छैक,\nतखन ओकरा के खाइत छैक?\nमाछी आ कीड़ा!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48922/size6/e4bc6289abe48e7d9f785620fc530683.jpg","text":"आ\nभूखल\nजंगली\nसूगर।\nघुर्र-घुर्र!\nघुर्र-घुर्र!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48931/size6/70c6baabb12b38c961f78078bfe0ccfe.jpg","text":"जखन\nहाथी जंगलमे\nपेखाना\nकरैत अछि,\nतखन के ओकरा चट कऽ जाइत अछि?\nगोबरक कीड़ा!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48933/size6/e43a74b0239462bf25802d946640cd5b.jpg","text":"आ\nभूखल\nजंगली\nसूगर \nघुर्र-घुर्र!\nघुर्र-घुर्र!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48925/size6/05089a3aefce21a5974a1f8f7b86f839.jpg","text":"जखन जमीनपर गाछक ठाढि, पात आ पानि खसै छैक,\nतऽ ककरा सभक लेल ई भोज भऽ जाइत अछि?\nदिबाङ आ कुकुरमुत्ता!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48926/size6/6712da7ee6bfe2b1ac0912e09764e94a.jpg","text":"आ भूखल जंगली सूगर।\nघुर्र-घुर्र!\nघुर्र-घुर्र!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48927/size6/36fefdc2bad5ae460bff3b65d5e0e241.jpg","text":"जखन धूआँसँ हवा प्रदूषित भऽ जाइत अछि,\nतखन ओकरा के सोखि लैत अछि?\nगाछ-बिरिछ!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48928/size6/126a5ea466b1124b1dc3e09d1b8bb663.jpg","text":"उम्म्म, मुदा भूखाएल जंगली सूगर नहि।\nघुर्र-घुर्र!\nघुर्र-घुर्र!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":129}}